# Completion Log Requirement

After completing any task, always create a report file with a brief overview of actions performed.

## File naming

- Use date and time in the filename.
- Filename must end with the word `log`.
- Example: `2026-03-09_22-10-05_sound_log.md`.

## Minimum report content

- Task objective.
- Files created/modified.
- What was implemented and why.
- Any checks performed (lint/tests/run status if available).
